cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.IR 

This paper discusses the use of IoT in the insurance industry, which involves the collection and analysis of large amounts of data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper may also fall under the category of Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CY) as it discusses the potential business model changes that may occur in the insurance industry. Lastly, the paper may also be classified under Software Engineering (cs.SE) as it discusses the challenges and strategies for implementing IoT in the insurance domain.
